Meant To Be

For her it was an unleashing. She had held in the desire, cupped it to her heart as if to seal it in place, restrict or restrain it. The price was an exhaustive effort and loneliness, a disengagement from her nature. When at last she opened, revealing heart and desire, it came forth with a fierce energy, all heat and power. She became unstoppable in her expression of her love, her passion. She became the woman she was meant to be. 

Midnight Musings by:
Tammi Brown
2018
